thread.title: Peter Legg
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by Peter Legg

author: Peter Legg
title: Peter Legg
text: The rep in BRISBANE was helpful efficient and made the process easy for relative novices. The car park was centrally located. Only issue was with the GPS which was out of date and could have done with updating given level of new roadworks we witnessed on the Pacific Highway. Drop off in Newcastle somewhat caught them off guard as I don't think they were expecting us. Overall very good experience and car was comfortable.and clean
